PrecisAmendments to the MIGRATORY BIRD SANCTUARY REGULATIONS which provide for the creation of the Gros Mécatina Bird Sanctuary on the north shore of the Gulf of St. Lawrence, redefine the boundaries of the Carillon Island and the Montmagny sanctuaries, and revoke the sanctuary status of six others in Quebec that will remain protected as National Wildlife Areas.

Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the MIGRATORY BIRD SANCTUARY REGULATIONS which provide for
the creation of the Gros Mécatina Bird Sanctuary on the north shore of the
Gulf of St. Lawrence, redefine the boundaries of the Carillon Island and
the Montmagny sanctuaries, and revoke the sanctuary status of six others in
Quebec that will remain protected as National Wildlife Areas.
